        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "MILTON AND THE BLUE HILLS",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Milton-a town of dignity and distinction!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "But modern Milton is something more than this, as old Milton was something more than this.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The rounded summits of the Blue Hills, to which the eye is irresistibly attracted before entering the town which principally claims them, are the worn down stumps of ancient mountains, and although so leveled by the process of the ages, they are still the highest land near the coast from Maine to Mexico.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "From them the Massachuset tribe about the Bay derived its name, signifying \"Near the Great Hills,\" which name was changed by the English to Massachusetts, and applied to both bay and colony.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000008_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000008_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Although its Indian name has been taken from this lovely range, the loveliness remains.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000008_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000008_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The Great Blue Hill, especially-the one which bears an observatory on its summit-swims above one's head.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "This is the view that the Governor so admired, and tradition tells us that when he was forced to return to England he walked on foot down the hill, shaking hands with his neighbors, patriot and Tory alike, with tears in his eyes as he left behind him the garden and the trees he had planted, and the house where he had so happily lived.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000010_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000010_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Here is the old, old garden, and although the ephemeral blossoms of the present springtime shine brightly forth, the box, full twenty feet high, speaks of another epoch.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000010_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000010_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Foxgloves lean against the \"pleached alley,\" and roses clamber on a wall that doubtless bore the weight of their first progenitors.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The avenue, however, was never completed, as Belcher was appointed governor of, and transferred to, New Jersey shortly after.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Two other men of note, who, since the days of our years are but threescore and ten, chose that their days without number should be spent in the town they loved, were Wendell Phillips and Rimmer the sculptor, who are both buried at Milton.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Not only notable personages, but notable events have been engendered under the shadow of these hills.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "How much of its success Milton attributes to its location-for one joins, indeed, a distinguished fellowship when one builds upon a hill, or on several hills, as Roman as well as Bostonian history testifies-can only be guessed by its tribute in the form of the Blue Hills Reservation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "This State recreation park and forest reserve of about four thousand acres-a labyrinth of idyllic footpaths and leafy trails, of twisting drives and walks that open out upon superb vistas, is now the property of the people of Massachusetts.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The granite quarry man-far more interested in the value of the stone that underlay the wooded slopes than in Ruskin's theory of its purifying effect upon the inhabitants-had already obtained a footing here, when, under the able leadership of Charles Francis Adams, the whole region was taken over by the State in eighteen ninety four.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "As you pass through the Reservation-and if you are taking even the most cursory glimpse of Milton you must include some portion of this park-you will pass the open space where in the early days, when Milton country life was modeled upon English country life more closely than now, Malcolm Forbes raced upon his private track the horses he himself had bred.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000016_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000016_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "You may see, too, a solitary figure with a scientist's stoop, or a tutor with a group of boys, making a first-hand study of a region which is full of interest to the geologist.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Circling thus around the base of the Great Blue Hill and irresistibly drawn closer and closer to it as by a magnet, one is impelled to make the ascent to the top-an easy ascent with its destination clearly marked by the Rotch Meteorological Observatory erected in eighteen eighty four by the late a Lawrence Rotch of Milton, who bequeathed funds for its maintenance.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "But as the eye grows accustomed to the stretching distances, objects both near and far begin to appear.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "We are six hundred and thirty five feet above the sea, on the highest coastland from Agamenticus, near York, Maine, to the Rio Grande, and the panorama thus unrolled is truly magnificent.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000018_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000018_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Facing nearly south, the long ridge of Manomet Hill in Plymouth, thirty three miles away, stands clear against the sky, while twenty six miles away, in Duxbury, one sees the Myles Standish Monument.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000018_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000018_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The next group to the right is in Lyndeboro.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000018_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000018_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "At the right of Lyndeboro, and nearly over the Readville railroad stations, is Joe English Hill, and to complete the round, nearly north northwest are the summits of the Uncanoonuc Mountains, fifty nine miles away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "This, then, is the Great Blue Hill of Milton.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Those who are familiar with the State of Massachusetts-and New England-can stand here and pick out a hundred distinguishing landmarks, and those who have never been here before may find an unparalleled opportunity to see the whole region at one sweep of the eye.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "From the point of view of topography the summit of Great Blue Hill is the place to reach.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "But for the sense of mysterious beauty, for snatches of pictures one will never forget, the little vistas which open on the upward or the downward trail, framed by hanging boughs or encircled by a half frame of stone and hillside-these are, perhaps, more lovely.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000020_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000020_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "So let us come down, for, after all, \"Love is of the valley.\" Down again to the old town of Milton.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000020_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000020_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "We have not half begun to wander over it: not half begun to hear the pleasant stories it has to tell. When one is as old as this-for Milton was discovered by a band from Plymouth who came up the Neponset River in sixteen twenty one--one has many tales to tell.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "That peculiar odor of sweetness which drifts to us with a turn of the wind, comes from a chocolate mill whose trade mark of a neat handed maid with her little tray is known all over the civilized world.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "And those mills stand upon the site of the first grist mill in New England to be run by water power.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "All ground is historic ground in Milton.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "That rollicking group of schoolboys yonder belongs to an academy, which, handsome and flourishing as it is to day, was founded as long ago as seventeen eighty seven.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000022_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000022_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "That seems long ago, but there was a school in Milton before that: a school held in the first meeting house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Nothing is left of this quaint structure but a small bronze bas relief, set against a stone wall, near its original site.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000022_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000022_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "This early church and early school was a log cabin with a thatched roof and latticed windows, if one may believe the relief, but men of brains and character were taught there lessons which stood them and the colony in good stead.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000022_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000022_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "One fancies the students' roving eyes may have occasionally strayed down the Indian trail directly opposite the old site-a trail which, although now attained to the proud rank of a lane, Churchill's Lane, still invites one down its tangled green way along the gray stone wall.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Yes, wherever one goes in Milton, either on foot to day or back through the chapters of three centuries ago, the Blue Hills dominate every event, and the Great Blue Hill floats above them all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248638_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248638/4813_248638_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "\"I will lift up mine eyes unto the hills from whence cometh my help,\" chants the psalmist.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "CHAPTER five",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "A strange procession, indeed, for a road originally marked by the moccasined feet of Indians, and widened gradually by the toilsome journeyings of rough Colonial carts and coaches.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Yes, New England has changed amazingly in the revolutions of three centuries, and here, under the shadow of this square plain building-Hingham's Old Ship Church-while we pause to watch the Sunday pageant of nineteen twenty, we can most easily call back the Sabbath rites, and the ideals which created those rites, three centuries ago.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The people are very proud of their new building.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The belfry is precisely in the center of the four sided pitched roof.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000007_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000007_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The original backless benches were replaced by box pews with narrow seats like shelves, hung on hinges around three sides, but part of the original pulpit remains and a few of the box pews.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000007_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000007_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "In sixteen eighty one the interior, like the exterior, is sternly bare.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "In the first place, they are well attended.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Every one is expected, nay, commanded, to come to church.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "In fact, after the tolling of the last bell, the houses may all be searched-each ten families is under an inspector-if there is any question of delinquents hiding in them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000009_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000009_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The congregation either waits for the minister and his wife outside the door, or stands until he has entered the pulpit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000009_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000009_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The small boys are separated from their families and kept in order by tithing men who allow no wandering eyes or whispered words.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "That they are interminable we know.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000010_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000010_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "This performance alone sometimes takes an hour, as there is no organ, nor notes, and only a few copies of the Bay psalm Book, of which, by the way, a copy now would be worth many times its weight in gold.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "After the morning service there is a noon intermission, in which the half frozen congregation stirs around, eats cold luncheons brought in baskets, and then returns to the next session.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "There is no idle talk or play.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The sermon is discussed and the children forbidden to romp or laugh.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "But is the message cheering?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "And yet, forlorn and tedious as the bleak service appears to us, there is no doubt that these stern faced men and women wrenched an almost mystical inspiration from it; that a weird fascination emanated from this morbid dwelling on sin and punishment, appealing to the emotions quite as vividly-although through a different channel-as the most elaborate ceremonial.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "It was this high pitch, attained and sustained by our Puritan fathers, which produced a dramatic and sometimes terrible blend of personality.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "It is easy to emphasize its absurdities, to ridicule the almost fanatical fervor which goaded men to harshness and inconsistency.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "It was religious zeal which furnished this motive power.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000013_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000013_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Those whom it now tortures with its hot pincers of doubt and self reproach are sacrificed to a cause long since won.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "And this moral stamina has marked New England ever since, and marked her to her glory.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "One cannot speak of Hingham churches-indeed, one cannot speak of Hingham-without admiring mention of the New North Church.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "These two small galleries, between the roof and the choir loft, held for thirty years, in diminishing numbers, negroes and Indians.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Hingham, its Main Street-alas for the original name of \"Bachelors Rowe\"--arched by a double row of superb elms on either side, is incalculably rich in old houses, old traditions, old families.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "Even motoring through, too quickly as motorists must, one cannot help being struck by the substantial dignity of the place, by the well kept prosperity of the houses, large and small, which fringe the fine old highway.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000016_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000016_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "And why not, when the very house is still handsomely preserved, where the nameless nobleman, Francis Le Baron, was concealed between the floors, and, as we are told in mrs Austen's novel, very properly capped the climax by marrying his brave little protector, Molly Wilder? Why not, when the Lincoln family, ancestors of Abraham, has been identified with the town since its settlement?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4813_248641_000016_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4813/248641/4813_248641_000016_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4813",
        "content": "The house of Major General Benjamin Lincoln, who received the sword of Cornwallis at Yorktown, is still occupied by his descendants, its neat fence, many windows, two chimneys, and its two stories and a half proclaiming it a dwelling of repute.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
